setBusGuideMultiColors(25.10)                    setBusGuideMultiColors(25.10)

Name
       setBusGuideMultiColors - Colors all the bus guides

Syntax
       setBusGuideMultiColors

       Colors  all the bus guides. Use this command to make it easy to distin-
       guish between different bus guide objects in the design.

       Specify resetBusGuideMultiColors to clear the bus guide colors.

Parameters
       None

Related Information
              * resetBusGuideMultiColors

              * Bus Planning chapter in the User Guide

                * Highlighting and Dehighlighting the Bus Guide

              * Edit Menu chapter in the Menu Reference

                * Bus Guide

